{"tid":1017194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《人日生日快樂》一人一個方法對付邊行路邊食煙嘅煙鏟","createTime":"2019-02-11T09:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T10:55:09.000Z","uid":147420,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"88ef872ea919629b54b0332d9a5443b3d2e02fac","tid":1017194,"uid":147420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"食煙其實無所謂，要食可以企定定食<br />\n但每次係街總會見到有啲邊行邊食煙嘅死煙鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n企係你地後邊就慘囉，一個唔好彩食正風就吸返哂你呼出嚟嘅二手煙<br />\n我先唔講健唔健康問題，而係成個過程好似質緊人食你痾出嚟舊屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你邊行邊食型啲咩？ 你唔試下邊跑邊食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  除左用我苦練十年嘅微波零步避開之外<br />\n究竟有咩方法可以對付佢老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1a4f97a9420ba23d45bd311bc2fab5e6057e5c","tid":1017194,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1yYRR9tOgJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1yYRR9tOgJE&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu184e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=ecb9433d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1yYRR9tOgJE</a>"},{"pid":"016ad256af08be21ea70000fffa1085a7e4ab00c","tid":1017194,"uid":147420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf1a4f97a9420ba23d45bd311bc2fab5e6057e5c","tid":1017194,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1yYRR9tOgJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1yYRR9tOgJE&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu184e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=ecb9433d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1yYRR9tOgJE</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipe